                     <interp inst="t18181028-12-verdict74" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 17.</p>
               <p>Of stealing to the value of 39s. only.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18181028-12-punish75" type="punishmentDescription">
